title: Spain 7 Year Note Yield
description: Spain 7Y was 2.67 percent on Thursday November 10, according to over-the-counter interbank yield quotes for this government bond maturity. Historically, the Spain 7 Year Note Yield reached an all time high of 10.04 in December of 1995. This page includes a chart with historical data for Spain 7 Year Note Yield.
author: Tesoro Público
